Uses of Package
com.fasterxml.jackson.xml.deser

Packages that use com.fasterxml.jackson.xml.deser
com.fasterxml.jackson.xml Package that contains XML-based backends which can serialize POJOs to and deserialize from XML, using Stax XML parsers and generators for XML processing and mostly standard Jackson data binding otherwise.
